<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Kubernetes on Notes</title><link>https://notes.harues.com/tags/kubernetes/</link><description>Recent content in Kubernetes on Notes</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2018 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://notes.harues.com/tags/kubernetes/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Change NodePort range local kubernetes</title><link>https://notes.harues.com/18/01/29/change-nodeport-range-local-kubernetes/</link><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://notes.harues.com/18/01/29/change-nodeport-range-local-kubernetes/</guid><description>&lt;h4 id="change-nodeport-range-local-kubernetes">Change NodePort range local kubernetes&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>Add following line to add following line to &lt;em>/etc/kubernetes/manifests/kube-apiserver.yaml&lt;/em>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">- --service-node-port-range&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>80-32767
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="examples">Examples&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">sudo vi /etc/kubernetes/manifests/kube-apiserver.yaml
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>